title: Arrow Midseason 5 Premiere: Who Are You? Photos Released
text:
Arrow Midseason 5 Premiere: Who Are You? Photos Released Russ Burlingame 
The CW has released a handful of promotional photos from "Who Are You," the upcoming midseason premiere of Arrow . 
You can check them out in the attached image gallery. (Also starring Stephen Amell as the Kool-Aid Man. OH YEAH!) 
Still reeling from the loss of Felicity's boyfriend and the apparent return of Laurel Lance from the dead, Team Arrow will redouble their efforts to track down Prometheus, the serial killer who has been terrorizing Star City as a way of getting back at Oliver, apparently for having killed his father as "The Hood" back in the show's first season. 
There's also a new quest set up to find the person who trained Oliver (likely Talia Head/al Ghul); Diggle's storyline is headed for a trial date; and a new ally will apparently join the fray.
